Package org.opendaylight.controller.sal.reader

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPluginInReadService
    The interface defines hardware view read methods to be implemented by protocol plugins
    IPluginOutReadService
    The interface defines hardware statistics updates service to be offered by protocol plugins
    IReadService
    This interface defines methods for retrieving the network node's flow/port/queue hardware view
    IReadServiceListener
    The interface describes SAL service to be consumed by functional modules that are interested in reader updates
